de.humatic.dsj.com

Class IAMVideoCompression

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.humatic.dsj.com.COMObject
      • de.humatic.dsj.com.IAMVideoCompression

  • public class IAMVideoCompression
extends COMObject
    Wrapper around the native IAMVideoCompression interface exposed by some VfW encoding and capture filters' output pins. Note that most more modern encoders will not expose this interface.
    To get an instance of this class, call COMFactory.queryInterface(...) with the codec filter and COMFactory.IID_IAMVideoCompression as arguments.
    For more information see MSDN documentation.
